	<presentation id="fixing-hal">
		<title>Let's Fix HAL!</title>
		<toc class="abstract">The <em>Hypertext Application Language (HAL)</em> has gained some popularity, but it also held back by design issues that make the language ill-defined. This is a call to action to fix HAL and get it to the point where it is well-defined and its definition can enter an open and broad review and standardization process.</toc>
		<toc class="resources"><a href="https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-kelly-json-hal" title='Mike Kelly, "HAL - Hypertext Application Language: A lean hypermedia type", September 2013'>HAL Specification</a></toc>
