			<slide id="housekeeping">
				<title>If it's broken, fix it</title>
				<ul>
					<li>HAL needs a fair bit of housekeeping</li>
					<ul>
						<li>A <q>HAL CURIE</q> is not a CURIE</li>
						<li>Embedded resources are underspecified</li>
						<li>Namespace (<q>CURIE</q>) mechanics are underspecified</li>
					</ul>
					<li>Community consensus on deployed code and design fixes</li>
					<ul>
						<li>(Some) breakage is unavoidable when fixing broken specifications</li>
						<li>Make the transition clear (it won't be clean)</li>
						<li>Provide test suites/tools to help with the transition</li>
					</ul>
				</ul>
